              </StackPanel>

              <sc:StrataMarkdown ShowTitle="True"
                                 Title="FizzBuzz Polyglot"
                                 Markdown="## Python&#x0a;```python&#x0a;for i in range(1, 101):&#x0a;    print(&quot;Fizz&quot; * (i % 3 == 0) + &quot;Buzz&quot; * (i % 5 == 0) or i)&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## JavaScript&#x0a;```javascript&#x0a;for (let i = 1; i &lt;= 100; i++)&#x0a;  console.log((i % 3 ? &quot;&quot; : &quot;Fizz&quot;) + (i % 5 ? &quot;&quot; : &quot;Buzz&quot;) || i);&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## C#&#x0a;```csharp&#x0a;for (int i = 1; i &lt;= 100; i++)&#x0a;    Console.WriteLine(i % 15 == 0 ? &quot;FizzBuzz&quot; : i % 3 == 0 ? &quot;Fizz&quot; : i % 5 == 0 ? &quot;Buzz&quot; : $&quot;{i}&quot;);&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## Rust&#x0a;```rust&#x0a;fn main() {&#x0a;    for i in 1..=100 {&#x0a;        match (i % 3, i % 5) {&#x0a;            (0, 0) =&gt; println!(&quot;FizzBuzz&quot;),&#x0a;            (0, _) =&gt; println!(&quot;Fizz&quot;),&#x0a;            (_, 0) =&gt; println!(&quot;Buzz&quot;),&#x0a;            _      =&gt; println!(&quot;{i}&quot;),&#x0a;        }&#x0a;    }&#x0a;}&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## Go&#x0a;```go&#x0a;package main&#x0a;import &quot;fmt&quot;&#x0a;&#x0a;func main() {&#x0a;    for i := 1; i &lt;= 100; i++ {&#x0a;        switch {&#x0a;        case i%15 == 0: fmt.Println(&quot;FizzBuzz&quot;)&#x0a;        case i%3 == 0:  fmt.Println(&quot;Fizz&quot;)&#x0a;        case i%5 == 0:  fmt.Println(&quot;Buzz&quot;)&#x0a;        default:        fmt.Println(i)&#x0a;        }&#x0a;    }&#x0a;}&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## Java&#x0a;```java&#x0a;public class FizzBuzz {&#x0a;    public static void main(String[] args) {&#x0a;        for (int i = 1; i &lt;= 100; i++)&#x0a;            System.out.println(i % 15 == 0 ? &quot;FizzBuzz&quot; : i % 3 == 0 ? &quot;Fizz&quot; : i % 5 == 0 ? &quot;Buzz&quot; : i);&#x0a;    }&#x0a;}&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## Ruby&#x0a;```ruby&#x0a;(1..100).each { |i| puts i % 15 == 0 ? &quot;FizzBuzz&quot; : i % 3 == 0 ? &quot;Fizz&quot; : i % 5 == 0 ? &quot;Buzz&quot; : i }&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## Haskell&#x0a;```haskell&#x0a;main = mapM_ putStrLn&#x0a;  [ if mod i 15 == 0 then &quot;FizzBuzz&quot;&#x0a;    else if mod i 3 == 0 then &quot;Fizz&quot;&#x0a;    else if mod i 5 == 0 then &quot;Buzz&quot;&#x0a;    else show i&#x0a;  | i &lt;- [1..100]&#x0a;  ]&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## Kotlin&#x0a;```kotlin&#x0a;fun main() = (1..100).forEach {&#x0a;    println(when {&#x0a;        it % 15 == 0 -&gt; &quot;FizzBuzz&quot;&#x0a;        it % 3 == 0 -&gt; &quot;Fizz&quot;&#x0a;        it % 5 == 0 -&gt; &quot;Buzz&quot;&#x0a;        else -&gt; &quot;$it&quot;&#x0a;    })&#x0a;}&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## Bash&#x0a;```bash&#x0a;for i in $(seq 1 100); do&#x0a;  [[ $((i%15)) -eq 0 ]] &amp;&amp; echo FizzBuzz || \&#x0a;  [[ $((i%3)) -eq 0 ]] &amp;&amp; echo Fizz || \&#x0a;  [[ $((i%5)) -eq 0 ]] &amp;&amp; echo Buzz || echo $i&#x0a;done&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## SQL (PostgreSQL)&#x0a;```sql&#x0a;SELECT CASE&#x0a;    WHEN i % 15 = 0 THEN 'FizzBuzz'&#x0a;    WHEN i % 3 = 0 THEN 'Fizz'&#x0a;    WHEN i % 5 = 0 THEN 'Buzz'&#x0a;    ELSE i::text&#x0a;END&#x0a;FROM generate_series(1, 100) AS i;&#x0a;```&#x0a;&#x0a;## C&#x0a;```c&#x0a;#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;&#x0a;&#x0a;int main() {&#x0a;    for (int i = 1; i &lt;= 100; i++) {&#x0a;        if (i % 15 == 0) printf(&quot;FizzBuzz\n&quot;);&#x0a;        else if (i % 3 == 0) printf(&quot;Fizz\n&quot;);&#x0a;        else if (i % 5 == 0) printf(&quot;Buzz\n&quot;);&#x0a;        else printf(&quot;%d\n&quot;, i);&#x0a;    }&#x0a;    return 0;&#x0a;}&#x0a;```" />
